data.description: ** SELLER PAID CONCESSIONS $3,000.00 - repairs, but down, closing costs ** If you are looking for a nice sized starter home this is the place for you!  There are 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, laundry room off the kitchen area, very spacious living room, kitchen and eating area, this property also offers a separate garage for parking or storage space. I almost failed to mention the Solar Panels are paid in full and a complete bonus to assist with utility bill! The property is settled on a nice dead-end street with a church building next door, close enough to walk to downtown area or to school! Enjoy the new splash pad park just down the road! There are always options to make more improvements and modifications to the existing creating your own special place! Come enjoy the front porch swings in the cool air for some coffee! Welcome home!
